Definition: Old Testament) the eldest son of Isaac who would have inherited the covenant that God made with Abraham and that Abraham passed on to Isaac
Example: he traded his birthright to his twin brother Jacob for a mess of pottage
Synonyms: son, i, noun, communication, Old_Testament, c, Old, Testament, the, eldest, of, Isaac, who, would, have, inherited, covenant, that, God, made, with, Abraham, and, passed, on, to, he, traded, his, birthright, twin, brother, Jacob, for, a, mess, pottage
Category: noun.person
